---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const post = {
  title: "How We're Using AI in Client Engagements Right Now",
  category: 'AI',
  publishedAt: 'December 3, 2025',
  readTime: '4 min read',
  excerpt: 'Practical applications, not hype. Where AI is actually saving time and improving output in our day-to-day work.',
};

const postId = 'POST-005';

const relatedPosts = [
  {
    id: 'POST-001',
    title: 'Why Most Service Businesses Fail Online (And What Actually Works)',
    excerpt: 'The common mistakes we see across every industry — and the framework we use to fix them.',
    category: 'Strategy',
    categoryColor: 'blue',
    publishedAt: 'February 12, 2026',
    image: '/images/blog/service businesses fail.png',
    slug: 'why-service-businesses-fail-online',
  },
  {
    id: 'POST-002',
    title: 'Why Most Google Ads Accounts Plateau After Month 3',
    excerpt: 'The structural patterns we see in stalled accounts, and the levers that consistently move them.',
    category: 'Paid Ads',
    categoryColor: 'green',
    publishedAt: 'January 28, 2026',
    image: '/images/blog/google ads plateau after month 3.png',
    slug: 'google-ads-plateau',
  },
  {
    id: 'POST-003',
    title: "Local SEO in 2026: What's Changed and What Still Works",
    excerpt: 'The tactics that have faded and the fundamentals that keep driving rankings for service businesses.',
    category: 'SEO',
    categoryColor: 'gold',
    publishedAt: 'January 14, 2026',
    image: '/images/blog/local seo in 2026.png',
    slug: 'local-seo-2026',
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout title={`${post.title} — Railshop Blog`} description={post.excerpt}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="hero-grid-svg" viewBox="0 0 1400 480" fill="none" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid slice">
        <line class="grid-line" x1="350" y1="0" x2="350" y2="480"/>
        <line class="grid-line" x1="700" y1="0" x2="700" y2="480"/>
        <line class="grid-line" x1="1050" y1="0" x2="1050" y2="480"/>
        <line class="grid-line" x1="0" y1="160" x2="1400" y2="160"/>
        <line class="grid-line" x1="0" y1="320" x2="1400" y2="320"/>
        <path class="corner-bracket" d="M 32 24 L 32 60 M 32 24 L 68 24"/>
        <path class="corner-bracket" d="M 1368 456 L 1368 420 M 1368 456 L 1332 456"/>
        <line class="tick-mark" x1="350" y1="468" x2="350" y2="480"/>
        <line class="tick-mark" x1="700" y1="468" x2="700" y2="480"/>
        <line class="tick-mark" x1="1050" y1="468" x2="1050" y2="480"/>
      </svg>
      <div class="hero-glow"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Corner annotations -->
    <div class="hero-annotation hero-annotation--tr" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="anno-code">SYS: BLOG</span>
      <span class="anno-sep">·</span>
      <span class="anno-coord">{postId}</span>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-annotation hero-annotation--bl" aria-hidden="true">
      <span class="anno-code">// ARTICLE DETAIL</span>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <!-- Breadcrumb inside hero -->
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/blog" class="breadcrumb-link">Blog</a>
        <span class="breadcrumb-sep">/</span>
        <span class="breadcrumb-current">{post.title}</span>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-inner">
        <div class="hero-left">
          <div class="post-meta">
            <span class="post-cat">{post.category}</span>
            <span class="post-meta-sep">·</span>
            <span class="post-date">{post.publishedAt}</span>
            <span class="post-meta-sep">·</span>
            <span class="post-date">{post.readTime}</span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-headline">{post.title}</h1>
          <p class="post-byline">By the Railshop Team</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content -->
  <div class="content-wrap">
    <div class="container content-grid">

      <!-- Article body -->
      <article class="main-col">

        <div class="content-block">
          <p>There's no shortage of takes on AI in marketing. Most of them are either breathlessly optimistic or reflexively dismissive. We're not going to do either.</p>
          <p>Here's where we're actually using AI in client work right now, what it's doing well, and where we still rely on human judgment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <h2 class="block-title">Content at the Right Scale</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="body-copy">For clients with location-based SEO strategies, we use AI to help build out service area pages at scale — not to generate thin, templated content, but to create a solid first draft that we then edit for accuracy, local specificity, and brand voice. What used to take a day per page now takes a fraction of that time, and the quality is higher than what most people could produce writing from scratch under time pressure.</p>
          <p class="body-copy">The same applies to ad copy variations. Testing headlines and descriptions across a large keyword set used to mean either cutting corners or spending hours on copy. AI handles the volume. We handle the judgment calls about what actually sounds right for the brand and the audience.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <h2 class="block-title">Research and Competitive Analysis</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="body-copy">AI tools have made competitive research significantly faster. Summarizing competitor positioning, identifying gaps in messaging, pulling patterns from a large set of search results — tasks that used to take hours of manual work are now much faster. We still verify everything, but the starting point is better and we get there faster.</p>
          <p class="body-copy">For client onboarding specifically, we use AI to process intake materials, identify key themes, and surface questions we'd want to ask in a discovery call. It's not replacing the discovery process — it's making us better prepared for it.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <h2 class="block-title">What We're Not Doing</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="body-copy">We're not using AI to generate final copy without human review. We're not using it to make strategic decisions about budget allocation, channel mix, or creative direction. We're not using it to write client-facing reports without significant editing.</p>
          <p class="body-copy">The judgment calls that actually matter — what's working, what to do next, how to talk to a specific audience — still require experience and context that AI doesn't have. What AI does well is reduce the time we spend on tasks that don't require that judgment, which means we spend more time on the ones that do.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <div class="block-header">
            <h2 class="block-title">The Honest Take</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="body-copy">AI is a productivity tool, not a strategy. The agencies and in-house teams getting real value from it are the ones using it to do more of the work that matters — not the ones using it to replace the thinking.</p>
          <p class="body-copy">If you're trying to figure out where AI actually makes sense in your marketing program, that's a conversation worth having. <a href="/contact#hubspot-meetings">Book a call</a> and we'll give you a practical take based on what we're seeing work.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Inline subscribe -->
        <div class="inline-subscribe">
          <div class="inline-subscribe-copy">
            <p class="inline-subscribe-prompt">Posts like this, weekly.</p>
            <span class="inline-subscribe-helper">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime.</span>
          </div>
          <form name="newsletter-signup" method="POST" netlify class="inline-subscribe-form">
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="newsletter-signup" />
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required class="inline-subscribe-input" />
            <button type="submit" class="inline-subscribe-btn">Subscribe</button>
          </form>
        </div>

      </article>

      <!-- Sidebar -->
      <aside class="sidebar">

        <!-- About -->
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <p class="sidebar-eyebrow">// ABOUT THE AUTHORS</p>
          <div class="sidebar-body-wrap">
            <p class="sidebar-body">Railshop is a boutique digital growth agency for service businesses. Everything we publish comes from direct experience managing paid media, SEO, and web programs for clients across HVAC, landscaping, home security, and more.</p>
            <a href="/about" class="sidebar-text-link">
              Meet the team
              <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--cta">
          <div class="sidebar-cta-status">
            <span class="sidebar-cta-dot"></span>
            <span class="sidebar-cta-label">Taking new clients</span>
          </div>
          <p class="sidebar-cta-heading">Work with us</p>
          <p class="sidebar-body">Book a no-commitment call to discuss your digital program and see what's possible.</p>
          <a href="/contact#hubspot-meetings" class="sidebar-cta-btn">
            Book a Call
            <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Back link -->
        <a href="/blog" class="sidebar-back-link">
          <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7"/>
          </svg>
          All posts
        </a>

      </aside>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Related Posts -->
  <section class="related-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="related-header">
        <span class="related-label">// RELATED READING</span>
        <div class="related-rule"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid">
        {relatedPosts.map((rp) => (
          <a href={`/blog/${rp.slug}`} class="related-card">
            <div class="related-image">
              <img src={rp.image} alt="" class="related-image-img" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
              <div class="card-hud" aria-hidden="true">
                <span class="hud-id">{rp.id}</span>
                <span class="hud-cat">{rp.category}</span>
              </div>
              <span class="img-corner img-corner--tl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="img-corner img-corner--tr" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="img-corner img-corner--bl" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="img-corner img-corner--br" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="related-content">
              <span class="related-date">{rp.publishedAt}</span>
              <h3 class="related-title">{rp.title}</h3>
              <p class="related-excerpt">{rp.excerpt}</p>
              <span class="related-cta">
                Read post
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
              </span>
            </div>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* ── Hero ─────────────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-grid-svg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .grid-line {
    stroke: var(--border);
    stroke-width: 1;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .corner-bracket {
    stroke: var(--border);
    stroke-width: 1.5;
    opacity: 0.35;
  }

  .tick-mark {
    stroke: var(--border);
    stroke-width: 1;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: -40px;
    left: -5%;
    width: 50%;
    height: 100%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 40%, rgba(56, 182, 255, 0.04) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .hero-annotation {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
    opacity: 0.4;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .hero-annotation--tr { top: 20px; right: 32px; }
  .hero-annotation--bl { bottom: 20px; left: 32px; }
  .anno-code { color: var(--blue); opacity: 0.8; }
  .anno-sep  { opacity: 0.3; }

  /* Breadcrumb */
  .breadcrumb {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 20px 0;
    font-size: 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .breadcrumb-link { color: var(--text-3); transition: color 0.15s; text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb-link:hover { color: var(--blue); }
  .breadcrumb-sep { color: var(--border-2); }
  .breadcrumb-current {
    color: var(--text-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  /* Hero inner */
  .hero-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    padding: 48px 0 60px;
  }

  .hero-left {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0;
  }

  /* Post meta row */
  .post-meta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .post-cat {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--blue);
    background: rgba(56, 182, 255, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(56, 182, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
  }

  .post-meta-sep {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--border-2);
  }

  .post-date {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--text-3);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .hero-headline {
    font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 44px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--text-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .post-byline {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-3);
    opacity: 0.45;
  }

  /* ── Content ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .content-wrap { padding: 64px 0 80px; }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .main-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 48px;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  /* Content blocks */
  .content-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .block-header {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
    padding-bottom: 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .block-title {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-2);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .body-copy {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .body-copy a {
    color: var(--blue);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  /* ── Sidebar ──────────────────────────────────── */
  .sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 88px;
  }

  .sidebar-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .sidebar-eyebrow {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 8px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    opacity: 0.65;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: block;
  }

  .sidebar-body-wrap {
    padding: 16px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .sidebar-body {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .sidebar-text-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.15s;
  }

  .sidebar-text-link:hover { gap: 9px; }

  /* CTA card */
  .sidebar-card--cta {
    padding: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    background: var(--surface-2);
  }

  .sidebar-cta-status {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
  }

  .sidebar-cta-dot {
    width: 5px;
    height: 5px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    animation: ctapulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @keyframes ctapulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50%       { opacity: 0.25; }
  }

  .sidebar-cta-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green);
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .sidebar-cta-heading {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-2);
  }

  .sidebar-cta-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: var(--blue);
    color: #111315;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-top: 4px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  :global([data-theme="light"]) .sidebar-cta-btn { color: #FFFFFF; }
  .sidebar-cta-btn:hover { opacity: 0.88; }

  /* Back link */
  .sidebar-back-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--text-3);
    opacity: 0.45;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 4px 0;
    transition: opacity 0.15s, color 0.15s;
  }

  .sidebar-back-link:hover { opacity: 1; color: var(--text-2); }

  /* ── Related Posts ────────────────────────────── */
  .related-section {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 56px 0 72px;
  }

  .related-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .related-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--blue);
    opacity: 0.65;
    white-space: nowrap;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .related-rule {
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .related-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .related-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--border-2);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .related-image {
    position: relative;
    height: 160px;
    background: var(--surface-3);
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .related-image-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.4s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover .related-image-img { transform: scale(1.03); }

  .related-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 18px 20px 20px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .related-date {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-3);
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  .related-title {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-2);
    line-height: 1.35;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover .related-title { color: var(--blue); }

  .related-excerpt {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-3);
    line-height: 1.75;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .related-cta {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 5px;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-3);
    margin-top: 4px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }

  .related-card:hover .related-cta {
    color: var(--blue);
    transform: translateX(3px);
  }

  /* HUD overlay */
  .card-hud {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(17,19,21,0.85) 0%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .hud-id {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: rgba(248, 250, 252, 0.5);
  }

  .hud-cat {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 9px;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-2);
    background: rgba(42, 47, 51, 0.8);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-2);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }

  /* Corner brackets */
  .img-corner {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    pointer-events: none;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .img-corner--tl { top: 8px;  left: 8px;  border-top: 1px solid var(--blue); border-left: 1px solid var(--blue); }
  .img-corner--tr { top: 8px;  right: 8px; border-top: 1px solid var(--blue); border-right: 1px solid var(--blue); }
  .img-corner--bl { bottom: 30px; left: 8px;  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blue); border-left: 1px solid var(--blue); }
  .img-corner--br { bottom: 30px; right: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--blue); border-right: 1px solid var(--blue); }

